title: Candy Jam.v3.Full.Game.Android.puzzle.apk
description:
Candy! Candies! Blend'em! Mix'em! Jam'em!
** You MUST play it to the last level -- twisted ending! **

Play as 'Jammie the Candy Master'.
Push the candies through the blenders into a jar - make yummy Candy Jam!
Mix different color candies!
Be careful: some blenders are designed to not only blend candy ;)

Controls:
- Swipe your finger on the screen to move UP, DOWN, LEFT or RIGHT.

#CandyJamGame
